This paper discusses systems for analyzing large scale dynamic graphs, which involves topics related to databases (cs.DB), data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on scalability and real-time potential also suggests a potential fit with the sub-category of scalable computing (cs.SI).
